[[File:Viktorija Daujotyte.jpg|thumb|right|300px]] '''Viktorija Daujotytė-Pakerienė''' is a Lithuanian literary critic and philologist.<ref>Viktorija Daujotytė in: ''[[Tarybų Lietuvos enciklopedija]]'', vol. 1 (A-Grūdas). – Vilnius: Vyriausioji enciklopedijų redakcija, 1985</ref><ref>[http://kultura.lrytas.lt/literatura/v-daujotyte-pakeriene-bandziau-tarsi-atsistoti-salia-s-neries.htm "V. Daujotytė-Pakerienė: „Bandžiau tarsi atsistoti šalia S. Nėries“"]</ref> She has written more than 30 scientific monographs, as well as essays and Lithuanian language textbooks for general education and higher education. She has also written about culture, feminism, and society. She was awarded the Lithuanian Grand Duke Gediminas, the fourth degree of the Order of the Lithuanian National Culture and Art, Unity, and National Progress, and other prizes.<ref>{{cite web|title=Viktorija_Daujotytė|url=http://kultura.lrytas.lt/literatura/v-daujotyte-pakeriene-bandziau-tarsi-atsistoti-salia-s-neries.htm|accessdate=10 December 2016}}</ref>
